data.description: Welcome to 10 Lincoln Ave, Newmarket, NH, where a recently listed residence transcends the ordinary, offering a riverside retreat designed for crafting cherished memories. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and over 1500 sqft of contemporary living space, this property is a haven that goes beyond being just a home. Nestled on a serene dead-end road, it provides not only comfortable living but immediate access to outdoor adventures. Imagine starting your day with a cup of coffee surrounded by the tranquility of nature, or picture yourself kayaking, canoeing, and fishing on the Lamprey River right from your backyard. The breathtaking views of the river become a daily backdrop to your routine, creating a unique blend of scenic beauty and practicality. Conveniently located within a stroll from downtown Newmarket's fantastic restaurants, this haven lets you embrace the vibrant local scene without sacrificing the tranquility of a riverside escape. Privacy is paramount on this peaceful dead-end road, offering a secluded haven to relax, unwind, and indulge in your passion for fishing, kayaking, or canoeing.  10 Lincoln Ave is more than just a property; it's an invitation to a lifestyle filled with comfort, convenience, and the natural allure of riverside living.
